                   varies by up to 40\% in a code translation task depending on
                   the prompt template, while larger models like GPT-4 are more
                   robust to these variations. Our analysis highlights the need
                   to reconsider the use of fixed prompt templates, as different
                   formats can significantly affect model performance.",
  month         =  nov,
  year          =  2024,
